Reported-by: Geert Uytterhoeven <geert@linux-m68k.org>
Signed-off-by: Rodrigo Siqueira <Rodrigo.Siqueira@amd.com>
---
 .../dc/dml/dcn31/display_mode_vba_31.c        | 20 +++++++++----------
 .../drm/amd/display/dc/dml/display_mode_vba.h |  2 ++
